               stealing, on the <rs id="t18280911-7-cd34" type="crimeDate">13th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-7-off33 t18280911-7-cd34"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 7s., the goods of 
